videos.description: Grayson Allen hits the tough layup at the buzzer to give Duke the thrilling 63-62 win over Virginia.
videos.headline: Allen adds to Cameron mystique with winner at the buzzer

videos.description: Grayson Allen breaks down his game-winning shot that beat No. 7 Virginia and what it means to him to fulfill his childhood dream to perform on the big stage of Cameron Indoor Stadium.
videos.headline: Grayson Allen: 'I just wanted to get to the rack'

videos.description: Check out the final seconds of Duke's win over Virginia, with the Cavaliers' Malcolm Brogdon scoring a go-ahead layup, followed by Grayson Allen driving to the other end to score an off-balance bucket at the buzzer.
videos.headline: Wild ending at Cameron Indoor
